summary: Ay * — grotesquely apologized for not being able to make it. Ay * – is an abbreviation for Eisen Leot recognition Oxy. Oxy is a symbol of the German spirit of freedom and freedom of expression. The word Oxy means "freedom" or "liberty" in German.
